Rendah Peringkat 3 di upacara penganugerahan!

299
00:19:46,850 --> 00:19:50,520
Tapi, memangnya apa itu Kesatria
Sihir Rendah Peringkat 3?

300
00:19:50,520 --> 00:19:51,330
Tak tahu.

301
00:19:51,330 --> 00:19:52,560
Eh?

302
00:19:52,560 --> 00:19:57,530
Padahal kalian sudah lama jadi Kesatria Sihir,
tapi kalian tak tahu apa itu?

303
00:20:00,110 --> 00:20:02,470
Itu peringkat Kesatria Sihir.

304
00:20:03,060 --> 00:20:05,870
Dan karena peringkat kalian tak pernah
berubah sejak bergabung jadi Kesatria Sihir,

305
00:20:05,870 --> 00:20:08,350
peringkat kalian masih
Kesatria Sihir Peringkat Lima.

306
00:20:08,350 --> 00:20:10,340
Sebaiknya mulai sekarang
kalian harus hormati Asta.

307
00:20:11,600 --> 00:20:15,140
Dan omong-omong, Charmy jadi
Kesatria Sihir Rendah Peringkat Satu.

308
00:20:15,140 --> 00:20:17,360
Berlututlah, para pecundang!

309
00:20:17,360 --> 00:20:19,460
Ha?

310
00:20:19,460 --> 00:20:23,990
Kalian harus ikuti
perintahku, Pecundang!

311
00:20:25,650 --> 00:20:28,990
Sepertinya, mereka terkesan karena
berhasil tangkap salah satu pemberontak!

312
00:20:29,470 --> 00:20:32,010
Meskipun bagiku lebih
terlihat seperti eksekusi mati.

313
00:20:35,940 --> 00:20:38,150
Sembahlah aku!

314
00:20:40,930 --> 00:20:43,180
Tarian aneh macam apa itu?

315
00:20:43,180 --> 00:20:45,130
Entah kenapa, tarian itu
terlihat sangat menyebalkan!

316
00:20:45,660 --> 00:20:48,100
Omong-omong, kerja bagus, Nak.

317
00:20:48,850 --> 00:20:51,680
Tapi, Komandan Fuegoreon...

318
00:20:51,680 --> 00:20:53,390
Ha, Fuegoreon?

319
00:20:53,860 --> 00:20:56,900
Kenapa kau khawatirkan
orang lain, dasar bodoh?

320
00:20:57,530 --> 00:21:01,530
Si raja bermuka serius nan temperamental
itu takkan mati semudah itu.

321
00:21:01,530 --> 00:21:04,400
Aku yakin dia pasti akan
kembali dan jadi lebih kuat.

322
00:21:05,330 --> 00:21:06,610
Tentu saja!

323
00:21:06,610 --> 00:21:11,650
Sip, aku juga akan berlatih lebih
keras dan jadi lebih kuat!

324
00:21:11,650 --> 00:21:12,660
Tidak, kau harus beristirahat.

325
00:21:12,660 --> 00:21:13,730
Ha?

326
00:21:13,730 --> 00:21:16,510
Kau terluka parah,
apa kau mau mati, dasar bodoh?

327
00:21:16,510 --> 00:21:19,420
Padahal justru Komandan yang mengirimku!

328
00:21:19,420 --> 00:21:21,290
Ya, kau harus beristirahat!

329
00:21:21,290 --> 00:21:22,410
Noelle ikutan juga?

330
00:21:22,410 --> 00:21:23,420
Kau itu bodoh, apa?

331
00:21:23,870 --> 00:21:25,130
Istirahat, ya.

332
00:21:25,130 --> 00:21:26,930
Istirahat, jadi kau sedang
senggang ya, Asta?

333
00:21:27,550 --> 00:21:29,300
Kalau begitu ayo kita ke diskotek!

334
00:21:29,300 --> 00:21:30,310
Ha?

335
00:21:30,310 --> 00:21:32,430
Diskotek?

336
00:21:32,430 --> 00:21:33,560
Kau harus bekerja.

337
00:21:33,870 --> 00:21:35,740
Akan kusiapkan segala sesuatunya!

338
00:21:35,740 --> 00:21:36,810
Sudah kubilang,
kau harus bekerja.

339
00:21:36,810 --> 00:21:38,910
Sepertinya hari ini aku
akan semakin sibuk!

340
00:21:38,910 --> 00:21:40,060
Aku pasti akan membunuhmu.

341
00:21:40,060 --> 00:21:42,820
